@startuml AD_D06_Receive_Acknowledge_Critical_Alert

title AD_D06 — Receive & Acknowledge Critical Test Result Alert

|Doctor|
|System|
|Lab Technician|

|Lab Technician|

note
  Prerequisites:
  - Doctor is authenticated
  - Lab test order exists for the patient
  - Result uploaded and flagged critical
end note

start

:Upload test result;\nFlag as Critical manually\nor system auto-detects\nout-of-range value;

|System|

:Create urgent alert record linked to:\n- Result\n- Patient\n- Requesting doctor;

fork
  :Send in-system notification;
fork again
  :Send email to doctor's\nregistered address;
fork again
  :Send SMS (if configured);
end fork

|Doctor|

:Receive alert via configured channels;
:Open patient record\nvia alert link;

|System|

:Display full result report\nwith critical value highlighted;

|Doctor|

:Review full result report;

if (Alert is a false flag?) then (yes)
  :Mark alert as "False Flag";\nAdd mandatory note;

  |System|

  :Audit-log false flag note;\nKeep original alert intact;
else (no)
  |Doctor|
  :Click "Acknowledge & Review";

  |System|

  :Timestamp acknowledgement\n+ record doctor ID;
  :Update alert status\nto "Acknowledged";
endif

|System|

if (Acknowledgement within\n30-minute window?) then (no)
  :Send second escalation alert\nto doctor;
  :Notify on-call supervisor;
else (yes)
endif

stop

@enduml
